  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThe seed phrase is displayed in two columns (words 1-6 and 7-12). The columns are rather far apart, which hints at reading \r\n them column by column, not line by line. This may lead to a wrong word order in the seed phrase backup.\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2023-11-14 16-21-26](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/7126627/ed261dab-662f-43b4-a6ff-6771850e9bb3)\r\n\r\nSuggested fix options: either bring the columns closer together, or reorder the words such that words 1-6 go into column 1, and words 7-12 to into column 2.",
